#META# contentSummary: A letter of complaint by the peasants from the villages of Khustgān and Angār about irregularities in the division of the yield of grapes and pomegranates by the landowner 's representative. The senders of the letter protest against the misconduct and unprofessional behaviour of the landowner 's representative, who was sent by a certain ʿAlī, possibly an employee of the landowner.
